<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[Cute apples in 1cm wedges, then soak in slightly salted water for 10m. Pat dry and leave on a tray.]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Make batter by beating eagg, adding flour, then corn starch and water]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[dip apple into batter, deep fry 1.5m then set aside]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Make toffee by melting sugar with ol, adding water carefully, then mixing in apple]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Serve with a bowl of iced water - people dip them in to solidify toffee]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
